# рџ“ќ TanStack Start Naming Conventions

## File Naming

### Components

```typescript
// вњ… Good - Use kebab-case for component files
// app/components/user-profile.tsx
// app/features/auth/components/login-form.tsx
// app/features/dashboard/components/stats-card.tsx

// вќЊ Bad - Don't use PascalCase for files
// app/components/UserProfile.tsx
// app/features/auth/components/LoginForm.tsx
```

### Server Functions

```typescript
// вњ… Good - Use kebab-case for server function files
// app/features/users/server.ts
// app/features/auth/api/server.ts

// вќЊ Bad - Don't use camelCase or PascalCase
// app/features/users/Server.ts
// app/features/auth/api/serverFunctions.ts
```

### Routes

```typescript
// вњ… Good - Use kebab-case for route files
// app/routes/users/$user-id.tsx
// app/routes/_auth/sign-in.tsx

// вќЊ Bad - Don't use camelCase or PascalCase
// app/routes/users/$userId.tsx
// app/routes/_auth/SignIn.tsx
```

## Function/Export Naming

### Server Functions

```typescript
// вњ… Good - Prefix with $ and use camelCase
export const $getUser = createServerFn()...
export const $updateProfile = createServerFn()...

// вќЊ Bad - Missing $ prefix or wrong case
export const getUser = createServerFn()...
export const $GetUser = createServerFn()...
```

### Component Functions

```typescript
// вњ… Good - Use PascalCase for component functions
export function UserProfile() {...}
export function LoginForm() {...}

// вќЊ Bad - Using other cases
export function userProfile() {...}
export function login_form() {...}
```

### Helper Functions

```typescript
// вњ… Good - Use camelCase for helper functions
function formatDate(date: Date) {...}
async function handleSubmit() {...}

// вќЊ Bad - Using other cases
function FormatDate(date: Date) {...}
async function handle_submit() {...}
```

